title: Evelynn Log-in
body:
It is beautiful. Thank you for the lovely music too! My favorite since Yorick relaunch

replies.body: so uh, am I the only one confused about who's wearing the crown in the back? She doesn't have a bow so I don't think it's Ashe.
I'm amazed at how much detail is in her thigh. Not even in a perverted way, there's just so much detail on her thigh it's absurd.
